") (wfw:commentRss nil "http://shawnblanc.net/2013/04/show-me-your-mic/feed/") (slash:comments nil "0"))) ("From the Archives: Diary of an iPad Owner" "<p>Three years ago this morning, I was standing in line at the Leawood Apple store, waiting to buy an original iPad.</p><p><a href=\"http://shawnblanc.net/2013/04/ipad-diary/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to 'From the Archives: Diary of an iPad Owner'\" class=\"glyph\">✚</a></p>" "http://shawnblanc.net/2010/04/diary-of-an-ipad-owner/" (20828 12143) new 6 nil nil ((title nil "From the Archives: Diary of an iPad Owner") (link nil "http://shawnblanc.net/2010/04/diary-of-an-ipad-owner/") (comments nil "http://shawnblanc.net/2013/04/ipad-diary/#comments") (pubDate nil "Wed, 03 Apr 2013 13:32:31 +0000") (dc:creator nil "Shawn Blanc") (category nil "Linked") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "http://shawnblanc.net/?p=11672") (description nil "Three years ago this morning, I was standing in line at the Leawood Apple store, waiting to buy an original iPad. ✚<a href=\"http://shawnblanc.net/2013/04/ipad-diary/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to 'From the Archives: Diary of an iPad Owner'\" class=\"glyph\">✚</a>
