") (wfw:commentRss nil "http://shawnblanc.net/2013/03/reading-into-google-readers-story/feed/") (slash:comments nil "0"))) ("“One of Gordy’s Camera Straps”" "<p>My first shot to ever make it on Flickr Explore.</p><p><a href=\"http://shawnblanc.net/2013/03/one-of-gordys-camera-straps/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to '“One of Gordy’s Camera Straps”'\" class=\"glyph\">✚</a></p>" "http://www.flickr.com/photos/shawnblanc/8576113368/in/explore-2013-03-20" (20811 28876) new 23 nil nil ((title nil "“One of Gordy’s Camera Straps”") (link nil "http://www.flickr.com/photos/shawnblanc/8576113368/in/explore-2013-03-20") (comments nil "http://shawnblanc.net/2013/03/one-of-gordys-camera-straps/#comments") (pubDate nil "Thu, 21 Mar 2013 20:42:52 +0000") (dc:creator nil "Shawn Blanc") (category nil "Linked") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "http://shawnblanc.net/?p=11631") (description nil "My first shot to ever make it on Flickr Explore. ✚<a href=\"http://shawnblanc.net/2013/03/one-of-gordys-camera-straps/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to '&#8220;One of Gordy&#8217;s Camera Straps&#8221;'\" class=\"glyph\">✚</a>
